Package reason.er.objects

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Concept<T,U>
    The Concept class is intended to model the behavior of ALC Concepts.
    Predicate<T,U>
    Abstract class that describes all Predicate Objects.
    QuantifiedRole<T,U>
    The QuantifiedRole is a representation of a role that is quantified over only one Concept.
    Quantifier
    The quantifier is simply an integer ID with a toString translation.
    Role<T,U>
    The Role class , unless ground instantiated, is not sufficient for use in Expression building.
    Term<T>
    This class is an attempt to allow different datatypes into the variable binding scheme.
